Package: gen3MetadataR
Title: User-Friendly Tools for Downloading and Manipulating Gen3 Metadata
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Joshua", "Harris", email = "harjo391@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides user-friendly tools for downloading, parsing, and manipulating metadata from Gen3 data commons within R. 
    The package enables authentication, fetching of metadata across different categories, and conversion of metadata into R data frames 
    for downstream analysis. Designed to simplify integration of Gen3 metadata into R-based workflows for bioinformatics and data science.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports: 
    base64enc,
    httr2,
    jose,
    jsonlite,
    magrittr,
    R6,
    stringr
